description:
As a user
  I can open order ticket panel
  So all functionality should work fine for the panel
name: Order Ticket panel

elements.name: Order Ticket Standard View - main functionality, stop/limit

steps.name: I am logged in to the application with default state
I add new 'Watchlist' panel in '2'nd tab
I click on 'buy' in the 'USD/JPY' market
the 'Deal ticket' panel should be visible
the order ticket standard view panel should contain items:
'hedging status' element text should be 'Hedging is OFF'
'submit button' element text should be 'Choose quantity'
the 'sell' button should be 'red' when it is clicked
the 'buy' button should be 'blue' when it is clicked
'submit button' element text should be 'Enter a price'
'submit button' element text should be 'Place Order'
open buy 'USD/JPY' order confirmation message should be correct
I add new 'Positions And Orders' panel in 'current' tab
